snippet: The latest gambit by Senator Joe Manchin III of West Virginia was an attempt to delay key parts of President Obama’s health care law.
abstract: Latest gambit by Sen Joe Manchin III of West Virginia is attempt to delay key parts of Pres Obama's new health care law; Manchin, centrist Democrat, has shown an impulsive, almost reflexive willingness to reject position of his leaders and try to entice fellow senators to a middle ground.
lead_paragraph: The latest gambit by Senator Joe Manchin III of West Virginia was an attempt to delay key parts of President Obama’s health care law.

headline.main: Senator Manchin Takes On Democratic Party Leaders in Pursuit of a Middle Ground
headline.print_headline: A Democrat Takes On Party Leaders, Seeking a Middle Ground
